== 个性 ==
阿南德被公众视为一个谦逊、亲善的人，并且因为其尽量置身政治和其它精神活动之外、集中精力研究国际象棋而广受赞誉。<ref name="niceguy">{{cite web |author=Hari Hara Nandanan, TOI Crest, May 15, 2010, 03.23am IST |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/more-sports/chess/Why-this-nice-guy-always-wins/articleshow/5933145.cms |title=Why this nice guy always wins |publisher=Timesofindia.indiatimes.com |date=2010-05-15 |accessdate=2010-11-11 |archive-date=2021-04-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210422051708/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/Sports/More-Sports/Chess/Why-this-nice-guy-always-wins/articleshow/5933145.cms |dead-url=no }}</ref>这为他在国际象棋界树立了一个深受喜爱的形象长达20年。可以作为佐证的是，[[卡斯帕罗夫|卡斯帕罗夫]]、[[克拉姆尼克|克拉姆尼克]]和[[马格努斯·卡尔森|卡尔森]]，这三位在其职业生涯中都曾与他争夺过世界冠军的棋手，分别都在他为2010年国际象棋世界冠军赛备战时助他一臂之力。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.chessbase.com/newsdetail.asp?newsid=6346 |title=Chess News - Anand in Playchess - the helpers in Sofia |accessdate=2010-05-19 |date=2010-05-19 |publisher=Chessbase |archive-date=2010-05-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100522043142/http://www.chessbase.com/newsdetail.asp?newsid=6346 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/more-sports/chess/Kasparov-Kramnik-came-to-Viswanathan-Anands-aid/articleshow/5951083.cms|title=Kasparov, Kramnik came to Viswanathan Anand's aid|date=2010-05-20|publisher=The Times of India|accessdate=21 October 2010|archive-date=2020-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200523063214/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/more-sports/chess/Kasparov-Kramnik-came-to-Viswanathan-Anands-aid/articleshow/5951083.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>阿南德有时又被称为“[[马德拉斯|马德拉斯]]之虎”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/india/3282237/Chess-world-title-Viswanathan-Anand-beats-Vladimir-Kramnik.html |title=Chess world title: Viswanathan Anand beats Vladimir Kramnik |last=Moore |first=Matthew |date=October 30, 2008 |work= |publisher=The Daily Telegraph |accessdate=July 6, 2010 |archive-date=2020-05-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200523063219/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/india/3282237/Chess-world-title-Viswanathan-Anand-beats-Vladimir-Kramnik.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>在2010年11月7日，由印度首相[[曼莫汉·辛格|曼莫汉·辛格]]为美国总统[[奥巴马|奥巴马]]举办的私人宴会中，阿南德是唯一获邀参与的运动员。[http://news.rediff.com/report/2010/nov/07/obama-visit-pm-hosts-private-dinner-for-obamas.htm] {{Wayback|url=http://news.rediff.com/report/2010/nov/07/obama-visit-pm-hosts-private-dinner-for-obamas.htm |date=20101110230937 }}

